    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA229-kiḷavi">1. itu talaimakaṉāṟ pirivuṇarttappaṭṭa tōḻi talaimakaḷai yāṟṟuvittuc colla vuṭaṉpaṭṭatu. 2. celavaḻuṅkuvittatūumām.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">1. This is how the confidante, who was informed by HIM of the separation, agreed to speak encouragingly to HER. 2. It is also how [she] prevents [his] going.</p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA229">
<l>            cēṟuñ cēṟu meṉṟaliṟ pulantu</l>
<l>            ceṉmiṉ ṉeṉṟal yāṉañ cuvalē</l>
<l>            cellā tīmeṉac ceppiṟ pallōr</l>
<l>            niṟatteṟi puṉcoliṉ ṟiṟattañ cuvalē</l>
<l>            yataṉāṟ</l>
<l>            ceṉmiṉ ceṉṟuviṉai muṭimiṉ ceṉṟāṅ </l>
<l>            kavaṇī ṭāta lōmpumiṉ yāmat</l>
<l>            tiḻaiyaṇi yākam vaṭukkoḷa muyaṅki</l>
<l>            yuḻaiyī rākavum paṉippō ṭamiyē</l>
<l>            kuḻaivāṉ kaṇṇiṭat tīṇṭit taṇṇeṉa</l>
<l>            vāṭiya viḷamaḻaip piṉṟai </l>
<l>            vāṭaiyuṅ kaṇṭirō vantuniṉ ṟatuvē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent2">When he says “we will go, we will go,” being vexed</l>
<l>I am afraid to say “go”.</l>
<l rend="indent2">If I say “don’t go,”</l>
<l>I am afraid</l>
<l rend="indent">because of the base words many people will throw on [his] breast.</l>
<l rend="indent4">Therefore,</l>
<l>go. Go [and] accomplish [your] work.</l>
<l rend="indent4">Having gone</l>
<l>beware not to delay there itself(?)<note place="foot">In this context, it seems impossible to take <term xml:lang="ta">ceṉṟāṅku</term> in the usual comparative sense. It is better to split <term xml:lang="ta">ceṉru</term>, <term xml:lang="ta">āṅku avaṇ</term>: "just there". T.V.G. even wants to take <term xml:lang="ta">āṅku</term> as an expletive here.</note>.</l>
<l rend="indent">Even if you are close [to her],</l>
<l rend="indent">embracing [her] so that you take the impression<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">vaṭu-koḷa</term>: thus T.V.G.’s explanation, and it makes sense at least.</note></l>
<l>of [her] jewel-adorned bosom at midnight, she is one to shiver alone.</l>
<l rend="indent2">After the young rain that played, [bringing] coolness,</l>
<l rend="indent3">gathering in the area of the softening sky(?),</l>
<l>have you seen the north wind too that has come to stay?</l>
    </lg>
      </div>
